  <brief_title>Ursofalk Tablets (500 mg) Versus Ursofalk Capsules (250 mg) in the Treatment of Primary Biliary Cirrhosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-blind, Double-dummy, Randomised, Crossover, Multicentre Phase IV Clinical Study Comparing the Effect of Ursofalk 500 mg Tablets od Versus Ursofalk 250 mg Capsules od on Liver Enzymes in the Treatment of Primary Biliary Cirrhosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
