  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy of Ursofalk 500 mg tablets versus
      Ursofalk 500 mg capsules in the treatment of Primary Biliary Cirrhosis (PBC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
