  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Negative pregnancy

          -  Signed informed consent

          -  Histologically proven non-cirrhotic liver disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  histologically proven cirrhosis

          -  PBC stage II+IV

          -  Positive HIV serology
      </textblock>
